{"tid":2252213,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GOT7榮宰被爆「毆打聽障同學」時間點卻大誤　JYP：確實有過衝突","createTime":"2020-10-21T10:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T22:41:40.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c41b31e9c78ebb6d6248e00ca4c11c7ae0b5b757","tid":2252213,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:29:13.000Z","msg":"南韓男團GOT7近日正在積極準備回歸，20日韓網卻出現爆料，爆料人自稱是GOT7成員榮宰的高中同學，因為有聽力障礙和智能障礙，在高中時經常被欺負，其中加害人之一就是榮宰。不過爆料的時間點和學校，和榮宰的經歷完全對不上，經紀公司JYP娛樂也在21日作出說明。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5218/d5218761.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5218%2Fd5218761.jpg&h=96c9b1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲榮宰被爆高中時霸凌同學，但他當時已轉學至首爾。（圖／翻攝自榮宰IG）<br />\n<br />\n爆料人表示，自己和榮宰是高中二、三年級的同學，多次被他勒索金錢和毆打，留下相當大的陰影。不過這說法被粉絲強烈質疑，因為榮宰高一雖然是就讀該爆料人所說的「木浦機械工業高中」沒錯，但他很快就因為成為練習生並準備出道，而轉學到首爾，高二和高三都是在「首爾藝術高中」就學，時間點和爆料者所說的並不相符。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5218/d5218762.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5218%2Fd5218762.jpg&h=1846b607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲榮宰平常經常做公益，性格善良，爆出「校園暴力」讓粉絲覺得很荒謬。（圖／翻攝自榮宰IG）<br />\n<br />\nJYP娛樂也在21日針對此事回應：「經過與榮宰確認，他確實和同學有過衝突，之後也確實沒有和解，但包括『校園暴力』這說法和文章的其他部分，全都不是事實。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5218/d5218760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5218%2Fd5218760.jpg&h=5a63b17a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲JYP娛樂回應，榮宰確實和同學有過衝突，但「校園暴力」不是事實。（圖／翻攝自榮宰IG）<br />\n<br />\nJYP娛樂也強調，雖然爆料人表示有透過電子郵件和公司聯絡，但事實上他們並沒有收到過任何相關郵件，「本公司已聯繫該篇文章作者，希望得到更確切和詳盡的內容做為確認，但至今都沒有收到回覆。我們將根據更明確的事實消息，採取正確的方式應對。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比錢化解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24dc9aaa9771774cf82a159081b6ba2357fa8b3a","tid":2252213,"uid":260437,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:31:15.000Z","msg":"偽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498a40153ef6f60987ad89095268ec626ef79ee1","tid":2252213,"uid":240447,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"我都準備打撚柒你"},{"pid":"019589a06d5e5e5d5edd56cbf5d20d60e8fe9ebe","tid":2252213,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"498a40153ef6f60987ad89095268ec626ef79ee1","tid":2252213,"uid":240447,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"我都準備打撚柒你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:46:08.000Z","msg":"WA 勁驚"},{"pid":"e5f96d4c73b58496fc2cabd18821a958d4caa31d","tid":2252213,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"收皮啦？"},{"pid":"1a80af57fbffbc358618e569b7dfccbbe7762c07","tid":2252213,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"498a40153ef6f60987ad89095268ec626ef79ee1","tid":2252213,"uid":240447,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"我都準備打撚柒你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:08:26.000Z","msg":"Gchi"},{"pid":"b89afaf1bf1a788331d147acaf73186d14daefbe","tid":2252213,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"jyp做乜認<br />\n順手打埋佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9032caf4bd96faf048e4f48903b9e6c63ccb376f","tid":2252213,"uid":176935,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:12:51.000Z","msg":"樣柒到完全唔知點做到idol"},{"pid":"1163de535e00798d2af0fc19324c4f3267c6a3b2","tid":2252213,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:24:36.000Z","msg":"關唔關JYP Daddy事？"},{"pid":"7273fb4f7d71c4a789821e3f09659b99e313c045","tid":2252213,"uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9032caf4bd96faf048e4f